io.toolisticon.annotationprocessortoolkit.tools.corematcher

Class CoreMatchers

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.toolisticon.annotationprocessortoolkit.tools.corematcher.CoreMatchers

  • public class CoreMatchers
extends Object
    Core matchers provided by the annotation processor toolkit which can be used for validation and filtering. This can be done in if statements or via the fluent apis for filtering and validation: FluentElementFilter and FluentElementValidator
